            innovation. My role focuses on software architecture, system design, and full-stack development with WPF and
            Blazor.
          </p>
          <p>
            I contribute to the early shape of the application by translating domain needs into software structure, using
            object-oriented modeling, visual mockups, and technical discussions to validate concepts with users and
            project partners. I also act as a technical contact with the
            <span class="redacted" aria-label="industry partner — withheld">industry partner</span> and contribute to planning
            and coordination.
          </p>
        </div>

